These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, biathlon, basketball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Sport   | basketball | cricket | tennis | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, frog, hamster
1. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Pet   | hedgehog | hamster | ferret | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, pall-mall, aristoff, cain
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fonseca-smoker is the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | cain | fonseca | aristoff | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, bridge, backgammon
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Game   | backgammon | billiard | bridge | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, march, may, april
1. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in may##2
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Birthday   | may | march | april | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, soy-milk, almond-milk
1. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | fanta | lemonade | soy-milk | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, paramedic, fisherman, scientist
1. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
2. the paramedic is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
3. the chef is between the paramedic and the scientist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | fisherman | paramedic | chef | scientist |

