.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, tomato, onion, cabbage
1. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
3. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | potato | cabbage | tomato | onion |

