3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Game   | backgammon | mah-jongg | monopoly | poker |

