.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, punk, jazz
1. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
2. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
3. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of d&b and the fan of jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2   |    3     |  4  |
| Music-Genre   | punk | jazz | dubstep | d&b |

